mastodon.core
Class Launcher

java.lang.Object
  mastodon.core.Launcher

public class Launcher
extends java.lang.Object

This class deals with processing input files and launching pruning algorithms in the GUI app. MastadonFrame knows the Launcher, the Launcher knows the trees.

Author:
justs

processFile

public boolean processFile(int burnin,
                           java.lang.String outgroupString)
                    throws java.io.IOException
Process a previously specified file. Apply a burnin and root on outgroup. Trees are loaded in batches of a 100 to save memory.

Parameters:
burnin - - first number of trees to ignore
outgroupString - - taxon to root the trees on
Returns:
true if the trees were successfully loaded
Throws:
